    "In the past century, the language changed enough that even native speakers of Turkish can no longer innately understand OT even in transliteration.",
    "Due to the differences between Ottoman and Modern Turkish, NLP tools developed for Turkish are not directly applicable for OT.",
    "As such, OT remains an underrepresented language in NLP.",
    "To this day, there is only one paper in the Association of Computational Linguistics (ACL) Anthology that primarily deals with OT (Özateş et al., 2024).",
    "Google's report on Gemini 1.5 (Team, 2024) includes some broad descriptions of the company's safety related concerns and decisions."
  ],
